&lt;p&gt;In an elegant, modern setting overlooking a garden knoll, Chef Sven Elverfeld creates Neue Deutsch cuisine that is both a visual and culinary delight. Aqua is placed&lt;strong&gt; #63 on the World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants 2016&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;list, &lt;strong&gt;#18 on Elite Traveller 2014 World&rsquo;s Top 100 List &lt;/strong&gt;and achieved &lt;strong&gt;3 Michelin Stars&lt;/strong&gt;. Attire is dressy. The Ritz Carlton has a special guest room rate for Diners Club International guests. Please inquire at the time of booking your dinner reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the Aqua website: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.restaurant-aqua.com/&quot;&gt;http://www.restaurant-aqua.com/&lt;/a&gt; or contact Aqua by phone at +49 (5361) 606056 or email at email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@restaurant-aqua.com&quot;&gt;info@restaurant-aqua.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time and a cell phone number or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MerchantRestaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
